---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 mt-auto">

  <!-- 主要內容 -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <!-- 品牌 -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-bold text-lg mb-3">
          <span class="text-xl">🛠️</span>
          <span>線上工具集</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          免費、安全的線上工具。所有處理都在您的瀏覽器中完成，檔案絕不上傳至任何伺服器。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 快速連結 -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">快速連結</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">首頁</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">關於我們</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">隱私政策</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 安全承諾 -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">安全承諾</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>檔案不上傳伺服器</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>無需帳號或註冊</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>完全免費使用</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <span>開源透明</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 底部版權列 -->
  <div class="border-t border-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500">
      <span>© {year} 線上工具集。保留所有權利。</span>
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-500 font-medium">
        <span>🔒</span>
        <span>100% 瀏覽器處理 — 您的檔案永遠不離開您的裝置</span>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

</footer>
